<h1>Income from Letting Property</h1>
<p>You recently told HM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) that you receive
income from letting property.</p>
<p>HMRC has an online learning package that tells you what you need
to do to meet your tax obligations as a landlord. The learning
package includes:</p>
<ul>
	<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.1cm">key dates for sending HMRC
	your tax return 
	</p>
	<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.1cm">when you need to pay your tax</p>
	<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.1cm">what records you need to keep</p>
	<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.1cm">how to work out your taxable
	profit</p>
	<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.1cm">what expenses you can claim</p>
</ul>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.1cm"><br/>
<br/>

</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.1cm">You can find more information <a href="http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/courses/syob2/letting/index.htm?WT.mc_id=LPC1">here</a>.</p>
